trans-unit.source: Instances of this class are passed to the <xref:System.Net.UploadDataCompletedEventHandler>.
trans-unit.target: 이 클래스의 인스턴스 <xref:System.Net.UploadDataCompletedEventHandler>.</xref:System.Net.UploadDataCompletedEventHandler> 에 전달 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the server reply to a data upload operation started by calling an <xref:System.Net.WebClient.UploadDataAsync*> method.
trans-unit.target: 호출 하 여 시작 하는 데이터 업로드 작업에 대 한 서버 회신 가져옵니다는 <xref:System.Net.WebClient.UploadDataAsync*>메서드.</xref:System.Net.WebClient.UploadDataAsync*>

trans-unit.source: You should check the <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Error%2A> and <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Cancelled%2A> properties before using the data returned by this property.
trans-unit.target: 확인 해야는 <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Error%2A>및 <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Cancelled%2A>이 속성에서 반환 되는 데이터를 사용 하기 전에 속성.</xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Cancelled%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Error%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Error%2A> property's value is an <xref:System.Exception> object or the <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Cancelled%2A> property's value is `true`, the asynchronous operation did not complete correctly and the Result property's value will not be valid.
trans-unit.target: 경우는 <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Error%2A>속성의 값은 한 <xref:System.Exception>개체 또는 <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Cancelled%2A>속성의 값은 `true`, 비동기 작업이 제대로 완료 되지 않았습니다 및 결과 속성의 값을 유효 하지 않게 됩니다.</xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Cancelled%2A> </xref:System.Exception> </xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Error%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Byte> array containing the server reply.
